Class AeRemoteDebugImpl.AeBreakpointListener

All Implemented Interfaces:
IAeProcessListener
Enclosing class:
AeRemoteDebugImpl
protected static class AeRemoteDebugImpl.AeBreakpointListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements IAeProcessListener

This is the global process listener stub which will forward breakpoint events to the remote event handler. Technically, this class listens globally for process events that indicate a breakpoint may have been hit. A test is performed and if so, an actual breakpoint event is generated.
